node.text:
I’ve partnered with @logitechc and @bluemicrophones for the launch of Creator Incubator: Up Next  

We want to see what lights your fire. We’re looking for vloggers, gamers, podcasters, and everything in between.

Contestants have a chance to receive some cash, gear, and the chance to meet me and some of my mentors!

Here’s how you can enter: 

☑️ Submit a video up to 60 seconds long that includes a brief intro and a clip of your choice showcasing your unique content.

☑️ Enter your submission + find more information at blueupnext.com  

☑️ Submissions are NOW OPEN until September 5th  -- good luck! #blueupnext
